test_large_range:
assert [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7] == [4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 4
  Left contains one more item: 7
  Full diff:
  - [4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
  + [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
test_even_range:
assert [2, 4, 6] == [8, 10, 12, 14, 16]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 8
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 14
  Full diff:
  - [8, 10, 12, 14, 16]
  + [2, 4, 6]
